00:34:36.262 --> 00:34:42.142
DataBot specifically is geared towards you still having quite a bit of control.

00:34:42.462 --> 00:34:47.662
So it could have just, like, done a bunch of analysis behind the scenes

00:34:47.982 --> 00:34:50.422
and then plopped it all in that Cordo report.

00:34:50.662 --> 00:34:54.061
But instead, how DataBot works is you sort of build up an understanding

00:34:54.061 --> 00:34:56.782
of the of the data alongside of it.

00:34:57.422 --> 00:34:59.142
You're keeping track of what's happening.

00:34:59.142 --> 00:35:00.262
