00:35:00.262 --> 00:35:02.982
You're, like, looking at these little summaries it gives you

00:35:03.422 --> 00:35:05.182
and you're exploring the data together.

00:35:05.182 --> 00:35:08.302
And then you might put the results in a QMD file.

00:35:08.622 --> 00:35:10.381
So this was a conscious choice.

00:35:10.381 --> 00:35:14.021
Like, we want the human to be keeping up with DataBot

00:35:14.182 --> 00:35:16.542
and for you to be, like, iterating together.

00:35:18.621 --> 00:35:25.542
And part of the reason is just so that, like, you can, you know, assess

00:35:25.542 --> 00:35:27.102
whether or not the analysis is correct.

