00:42:04.422 --> 00:42:09.381
where you need to sort of be involved frequently so that you can understand your data.

00:42:09.381 --> 00:42:13.542
I'm OK with like if I know what I want to go into the shiny app, I'm generally OK with

00:42:13.542 --> 00:42:18.262
Posit Assistant or something similar to just go and take what I know about the data and

00:42:18.262 --> 00:42:21.221
put it into a shiny app relatively autonomously.

00:42:22.661 --> 00:42:29.061
One reason is that like it is easy to verify for both computers and humans if the shiny

00:42:29.061 --> 00:42:29.781
