00:42:46.502 --> 00:42:52.581
it like while it's running the app for the first time or like if it produces an error

00:42:52.581 --> 00:42:54.422
and then I ask it to fix something.

00:42:54.422 --> 00:42:58.102
So it's easy to generally easy to verify if it's working.

00:42:58.102 --> 00:43:05.701
Whereas something like a data analysis where it's often harder to tell for the LLM or for

00:43:05.701 --> 00:43:08.661
you as the person quickly if it is done correctly.

00:43:08.661 --> 00:43:10.901
So you often need more human involvement.

