00:47:28.661 --> 00:47:35.461
And so because of that, one thing that is important are either providing guardrails

00:47:35.461 --> 00:47:42.422
for the assistant or for adding additional information through a customization.

00:47:42.422 --> 00:47:49.062
So we already saw one way that you can do that by creating this MD file for the agent

